{
  "stem": "5371.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And all the other people were taken away also, to Birkenau, because the railroad station was in between Auschwitz and Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We came to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They put us up in a big place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then they took us into shower rooms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They shaved us, took all our clothes away, naturally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They put us up with kind of stinky liquid, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was disinfectant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then they tattooed our numbers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "76344.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were-- they were doing it alphabetically, so I-- I must have been-- because my name is K, so I got this number, because there were previous numbers and there were later numbers, because they were going up to the last letter-- to W, Z.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, when they did the tattooing, it hurt, you know, because they go with needles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At first, it's-- it's bloody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then it becomes blue, the way it is now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I just like twitched my head, and I was hit in the head by a hand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was very hard, because I moved my head, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After everything was done, they put us up into different blocks, different buildings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were put into 7A with a group of young people, all young people, which was the upper part of the building.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was 7 and 7A.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we were on the top, on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The head of the block was a German of Polish descent, which was named Alfred Olshevsky.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he was screaming and yelling and kicking and beating.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And each one was assigned to a bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were triple beds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they showed us where the washroom is.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
